'''格鲁吉亚使徒自主正教会'''（{{lang-ka|საქართველოს სამოციქულო ავტოკეფალური მართლმადიდებელი ეკლესია}}）是一個獨立的[[東正教自主教會|東正教自主教會]]。位於[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]]，信眾多是當地的[[格魯吉亞人|格魯吉亞人]]，為格魯吉亞的[[國教會|國教會]]；直到1921年憲改後，此政教合一情形才改變。信徒聲稱，該會歷史根源可以追溯到公元4世紀。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.fed-soc.org/publications/detail/a-retrospective-on-the-1921-constitution-of-the-democratic-republic-of-georgia |title = A Retrospective on the 1921 Constitution of the Democratic Republic of Georgia |publisher =  |accessdate = 5 March 2015 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170703172653/http://www.fed-soc.org/publications/detail/a-retrospective-on-the-1921-constitution-of-the-democratic-republic-of-georgia |archive-date = 2017-07-03 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>
格魯吉亞使徒自主正教會與其他[[東正教自主教會|東正教自主教會]]完全[[共融|共融]]。包括[[君士坦丁堡普世牧首|君士坦丁堡普世牧首]]在內，其自主權受到其他正教會的認可。如同其他正教會的架構，其最高管理機構是[[圣主教公會|圣主教公會]]，由[[全格魯吉亞的卡托利科斯及大牧首|全格魯吉亞的卡托利科斯及大牧首]]領導。現任格魯吉亞大牧首為[[格魯吉亞的伊利亞二世|格魯吉亞的伊利亞二世]]。他於1977年當選。根據2013年的一項調查表明，格魯吉亞正教會在格魯吉亞是最受信任的機構，包括95%的受訪者對教會的工作表示認可。其在公共事務的影響力使之成為格魯吉亞最有權勢的機構之一。<ref>{{cite news |last=Funke |first=Carolin |title=The Georgian Orthodox Church and its Involvement in National Politics |url=http://www.cacianalyst.org/publications/analytical-articles/item/13023-the-georgian-orthodox-church-and-its-involvement-in-national-politics.html |agency=[[Central_Asia-Caucasus_Institute|Central Asia-Caucasus Institute]] Analyst |date=14 August 2014 |quote=After the dissolution of the Soviet Union, the Georgian Orthodox Church (GOC) emerged as Georgia’s most respected and influential institution. |accessdate=2016-03-02 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305212530/http://www.cacianalyst.org/publications/analytical-articles/item/13023-the-georgian-orthodox-church-and-its-involvement-in-national-politics.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Rimple |first=Paul |title=Russia: Sochi Bets on Becoming the Black Sea Monte Carlo |url=http://www.eurasianet.org/node/71051 |work=eurasianet.org |agency=[[Open_Society_Institute|Open Society Institute]] |date=21 November 2014 |quote=The Georgian Orthodox Church, the country’s most influential institution... |accessdate=2016-03-02 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060034/http://www.eurasianet.org/node/71051 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 現狀 ==
1990年3月3日，[[君士坦丁堡普世牧首|君士坦丁堡普世牧首]]正式承認并批准了格魯吉亞教會的自主權。此外，牧首也被授予了[[卡托利科斯|卡托利科斯]]的稱號。此後的格魯吉亞獨立使教會得到極大的復興。在格魯吉亞憲法第九條中，說明了格魯吉亞正教會在該國歷史中起到的特殊作用。<ref>{{PDFlink|[http://www.parliament.ge/files/68_1944_951190_CONSTIT_27_12.06.pdf Constitution of Georgia - Official English translation]}}</ref>在2002年10月14日，伊利亞二世與格魯吉亞總統[[爱德华·谢瓦尔德纳泽|爱德华·谢瓦尔德纳泽]]簽署的協定中，教會與國家的關係進一步得到定義。協議引人注目地承認了格魯吉亞正教會對該國所有教堂及修道院的所有權，並且賦予其在政府中的參議角色。尤其是在教育方面。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.patriarchate.ge/?action=text/samartali05|title=საქართველოს საპატრიარქოს ოფიციალური ვებ-გვერდი|publisher=|accessdate=5 March 2015|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807003208/https://patriarchate.ge/?action=text%2Fsamartali05|dead-url=no}}</ref>
